js.dynamic
Class JSQueue<E>

java.lang.Object
  js.dynamic.JSQueue<E>

public class JSQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object

A basic implementation of the 'Queue' dynamic structure, which adheres to the First In, First Out principle. Data can only be added to the end of the queue, and can only be removed from the start of the queue, in the order it was added.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Josh
